    "body": "## Purpose\n\nRefactor for the codebase, reuse `swizzle_blockscale` and `cutlass_fp4_supported`\n\nThis PR is safe, it doesn't change any logic, for easier review.\n\nWill have another PR adding Flashinfer to Compressed Tensor MOE\n\n## Test\n\n`lm_eval  --model vllm  --model_args \"pretrained=nm-testing/Qwen3-30B-A3B-NVFP4,max_model_len=32768,enable_expert_parallel=True,enforce_eager=True\"  --trust_remote_code  --tasks gsm8k  --num_fewshot 5  --batch_size auto`\n\n```bash\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8779|±  |0.0090|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8757|±  |0.0091|\n```",
    "created_at": "2025-07-25T19:02:33Z",
